556acf7","tid":1229800,"uid":13504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"學歷低不是罪過 問題係佢地唔腳踏實地做人<br />\n情願出賣良心去換取佢要努力起碼5 年以上的時間先換到的人工<br />\n好多人小學都未讀過 但佢地知自己咩料 應該行點樣嘅路"},{"pid":"fa7f437154e433b49c9823ad817558f7cb3e77c7","tid":1229800,"uid":194177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4da8a8ee24cf5b2c53d1f42267f938eda30d4a6","tid":1229800,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44b8828d5703934937f073f8cc7484888e02bb1f","tid":1229800,"uid":197157,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"有人話應該提高招聘條件（例：大專）<br />\n根本唔可能，因為政府本意就係搵一班智商低嘅人去操縱<br />\n係人都知扯線公仔愈冇思想係愈好，邊個會想畀公仔反噬？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"一直以嚟就係咁"},{"pid":"dcfa3f6cc69a0220c4ca18d67384bea8b40217ee","tid":1229800,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"我都係低學歷又唔見我奶共"},{"pid":"c9de24324e7960a1c578c7bcfa029ceda7635ba7","tid":1229800,"uid":197157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcfa3f6cc69a0220c4ca18d67384bea8b40217ee","tid":1229800,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"我都係低學歷又唔見我奶共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"所以招聘本身已經係一個篩選過程<br />\n同樣係低學歷，有人不屑做，就算人工明顯高都唔做<br />\n噉淨低仍然會做嘅就係：1. 錢＞良心　2. 冇良心<br />\n所以話叫班狗回頭是岸&hellip;&hellip;可能有用，但萬中無一囉"},{"pid":"8f5fbdc67d231461450a5654b2716cd6c7180488","tid":1229800,"uid":71044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824745d02a90d279f802ae6d9a934439c784832d","tid":1229800,"uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61ef8da7e10c5bf4fc4a49f9d980e9b8673a4373","tid":1229800,"uid":170309,"like":2,"dislike":0